Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太優秀了 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為我們櫻蘭的特優生再適合不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太優秀了 也成問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後的方向 考試什麼的都自己決定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.11,0:02:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其結果就是直到今天來辦理入學手續
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都她一個人完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以爸爸你不用來也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.93,0:02:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 春緋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前還有一些事要和你父親談
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.05,0:02:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁這段時間你去參觀下學校如何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.38,0:02:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是正值暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.26,0:02:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒什麼人在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入學手續爸爸會認真辦理的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子太出色的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反之父母會覺得更寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡說不定會比較開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對沒有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是個玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不可思議王國的春緋-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛痛……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 拿不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壺拿不下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.49,0:04:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幫一下忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:43.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.73,0:04:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失……不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子是從什麼地方來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.36,0:05:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此看來 出口的話……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有那扇門了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香蕉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:45.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是游泳池？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.48,0:06:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是哭了很長時間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.36,0:06:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:57.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這泳池的水是你至今為止在心中所流的淚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦的回憶 難過的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都一直忍受著……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是快點上來比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然會被吃掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 剛才的那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要快點變回原來的身高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是已經變回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一方變大 則另一方變小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可絕對不容易哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.77,0:07:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 有客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:08:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問能不能讓我們拿些蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 月末結算
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在金錢方面管理很詳細呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那本筆記中都記些什麼內容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是全部內容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你是第一次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會這麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…好像有點理解錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬰兒好像自己爬走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 摔倒了 摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是公爵夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.68,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊做香蕉湯的是我的廚師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躺著的是我的小貓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.17,0:09:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道貓咪會偷笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.00,0:09:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼說我是廚師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:42.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便差遣我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.04,0:09:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們自己在旁邊偷閒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環 你這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個孩子的母親是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很在意這個孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能找到媽媽真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和媽媽在一起比什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.56,0:10:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我差不多要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能幫我照看他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.50,0:10:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被邀請去聽最終審判的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審判？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真認為這個玩偶是公爵夫人的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 貓先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.73,0:11:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃驚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會像現在這樣……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒出現一會兒消失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想請教……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該往哪裡走才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要看…你想往哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原先來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒覲見女王陛下就想回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是絕不允許的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下…是這個世界的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說話聽起來實在太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個出來把話說清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個…什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.05,0:12:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能早點回來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有位子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.61,0:12:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 沒有位子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位子……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不要隨便插話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.17,0:13:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡還有這麼多位子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想請教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.89,0:13:24.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你頭髮還真長呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.69,0:13:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很喜歡你這長髮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但實際你的頭髮應該很短的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能先不要管我頭髮長短的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.76,0:13:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天穿的是裙子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說我都是個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了怎麼樣都行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣吃甜食…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長蛀牙的話我可不管哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要好好刷牙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.12,0:14:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打鼾超人好遜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:02.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜謎時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜謎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金槍魚和中段為什麼相似
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 完全不對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.93,0:14:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然平民就是平民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要來杯葡萄酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.69,0:14:24.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未成年人不得飲酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她演愛麗絲果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有點不太適合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.49,0:14:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡一直都處於下午3點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直都是下午茶時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問這裡到底是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.70,0:15:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是和爸爸到櫻蘭學院辦理入學手續的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.80,0:15:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜謎時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.69,0:15:10.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸和我有相似處 這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個相像嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是櫻蘭學院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入學後你打算做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你進入櫻蘭後打算做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.89,0:15:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼？！當然是讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.56,0:15:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就光讀書嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.05,0:15:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有想要實現的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.48,0:15:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入櫻蘭學習就是為了達成這個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好偉大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想實現的夢想指的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.77,0:15:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來我……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是學生生活並不僅僅只有學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.33,0:15:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那其他還有什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然還有很多…有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.60,0:16:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.74,0:16:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審判開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,審判？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公爵夫人被處以死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.93,0:16:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅因為女王陛下心血來潮…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這絕對不允許
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春不管是不是在夢中都是一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被告 公爵夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到我們音樂會的邀請而來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對以上的罪名都認可嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這能算是罪名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我是被告的辯護律師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在社交場合登場這是我的工作 國王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.65,0:17:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就可放任不管自己的孩子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯在說是為了工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓孩子一個人寂寞得呆在家中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 女王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.38,0:17:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不正確的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母真得很忙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為孩子的對此是能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不會怨恨他人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真地將她處以死刑的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.39,0:18:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是神聖的法庭決不講人情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不講人情的話全權交給機器人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法庭 辯護律師這些根本不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太囂張了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到是你具有辯護權嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身就是個罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好 我們就先審訊你這個辯護律師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:40.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的罪責？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你打碎的花瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是那個時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:54.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那時並沒有碎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候確實沒有碎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.97,0:18:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是打碎這花瓶的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了打碎花瓶的不是……我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證人……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於辯護律師的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的請出來作證
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.04,0:19:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可作證 國王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是剛才的……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人在學習性格方面都不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習 學習 還是學習
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都沒有一點有趣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你過得太輕閒了 環學長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.06,0:19:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:01.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會知道他的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還知道我們是雙生子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道我的筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我長蛀牙的事你也很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.08,0:20:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有這麼好朋友 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.52,0:20:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 讓你吃了不少苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可要好好把握現在的學院生活哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.65,0:21:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春緋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.24,0:21:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難得啊 你也會午睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.73,0:21:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多到營業時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像夢般的學院生活…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真是無法區分呢 現實和夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興點 春緋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們櫻蘭男公關部即將接受媒體的採訪了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.91,0:23:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是接受學院新聞社的採訪而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:15.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集《採訪傳說中的男公關部》
